nodes.text: Vennie was a female individual who during the Atterra campaign served as the pilot of the MG-100 StarFortress SF-17 Crimson Cutter. On occasion Vennie flew in an a-wing starfighter as an escort for the bombers. After the campaign, Vennie was assigned by Vice Admiral Amilyn Holdo to pilot a starfighter for the Resistance during the evacuation of their base on D'Qar.
